{
  "stem": "1292.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They was catching people for what they did call transports.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did live in the same building, but two story higher than my mother and my sister and my family and my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when the transport was-- I heard-- when the people was called to transport, I heard that my mother and my sister was in this.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They was congregating them on a big place together surrounded by police and not to escape.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember this incident very vividly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I did find out that they are in a transport, I was very disturbed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went to this place, and there was a lot of police-- SS people there and Gestapo people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I went to this what then was the chief of the Gestapo in this-- for this aktion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was with a dog and, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I wasn't scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All I did think, how to take them out from the transfer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I approach him, and he look at me and he spoke to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, of course, the other people was then daring to try to approach him as well.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And for some strange reason he would talk to me and shoot in my presence everybody who did want to approach him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was a terrible experience for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he took me what it was called then a [NON-ENGLISH], which was this police station.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- because those people who did have the stamp-- what was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that means some-- it was a document which identify you with a allowance to stay in Krakow in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this stamp was so important because without the stamp, you didn't have the chance to stay.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
